Package: bio.plotting
Title: Simple tools for creating maps and quickly plotting data
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c( person("Mike", "McMahon", email="mike.mcmahon@dfo-mpo.gc.ca", role=c("aut", "cre")) )
Description: This package facilitates the creation of basemaps in any projection.  Dataframes can also be overlain easily, displayed either generically, or as a number of discrete classes depending on the
  value of a particular field.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0),
    mapdata
Imports:
    classInt,
    grDevices,
    graphics,
    maps,
    maptools,
    rgeos,
    sp
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/Beothuk/bio.plotting/
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
